               <p>THOMAS CLARK SIDWELL. I live at <placeName id="t18340410-164-crimeloc937">Cranford</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18340410-164-crimeloc937" type="placeName" value="Cranford"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18340410-164-crimeloc937" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340410-164-off935 t18340410-164-crimeloc937"></join> - the prisoner was in my service, and left on the 3d of April - I saw her in her lodging in Brentford, on Tuesday, the 8th of April - and asked her for the property - she said she had none - I said she had, and if she did not give them up I would give her to the officer - I found some of the things at her lodging at Brentford, which I gave to the officer - he received the rest of the things from my wife.</p>
               <p>
            
